<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Board QR Code – Python Adventure Quest</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      background: #fff;
      color: #000;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .subtitle { color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .qr-box {
      border: 3px solid #000;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .qr-box img { display: block; width: 280px; height: 280px; }
    .instructions {
      max-width: 380px;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .instructions strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .instructions ol { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .url {
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: #777;
      word-break: break-all;
      max-width: 380px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .no-print-area { margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .print-btn {
      padding: 0.75rem 2.5rem;
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }
    .print-btn:hover { background: #333; }
    .back-link { color: #555; font-size: 0.85rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    @media print {
      .no-print-area { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>🐍 Python Adventure Quest</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Physical Board — Card Space QR Code</p>

  <div class="qr-box">
    <img src="<%= qrDataUrl %>" alt="Board QR Code">
  </div>

  <div class="instructions">
    <strong>How to use this QR code:</strong>
    <ol>
      <li>Print this page and cut out the QR code box</li>
      <li>Stick it onto the physical game board</li>
      <li>When a player lands on a <strong>📜 Card Space</strong>, they scan this QR with their phone</li>
      <li>The app automatically draws a random card for them</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <p class="url"><%= scanUrl %></p>

  <div class="no-print-area">
    <button class="print-btn" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Print This Page</button>
    <a class="back-link" href="/game/lobby">← Back to Lobby</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
